[Agent Hickley] Dr. Cross,
you might want to see this.

1456
02:14:51,392 --> 02:14:54,361
- This was Megars desk?
- Yeah.

1457
02:14:54,428 --> 02:14:57,397
- What are you doing?
- Scoping GIFs.

1458
02:14:57,465 --> 02:15:01,925
Graphic Interchange Formats.
