1459
02:15:02,003 --> 02:15:05,131
Somewhere among the billions of
zeros and ones making this image...

1460
02:15:05,206 --> 02:15:08,369
- is a string of text.
- I know about this.

1461
02:15:08,442 --> 02:15:10,876
