of passing notes in class.

1462
02:15:10,945 --> 02:15:13,004
It's driving the teachers nuts.

1463
02:15:13,080 --> 02:15:16,072
How long before
you can access it?

1464
02:15:16,150 --> 02:15:18,209
Try never.

1465
02:15:18,286 --> 02:15:20,345
You don't crack Stego
without a password.

1466
02:15:20,421 --> 02:15:22,389
Would you take me
to his office?

1467
02:15:26,761 --> 02:15:29,696
Oh. When you find Soneji.
Ask him for the password.

1468
02:15:29,764 --> 02:15:33,200
He planted a monitoring virus
on the girl's hard drive.

1469
02:15:33,267 --> 02:15:37,203
Every keystroke Megan hit.
Soneji was recording it.

1470
02:15:37,271 --> 02:15:39,364
[Computer Beeping]

1471
02:15:43,544 --> 02:15:46,138
Good move. Jezz.

1472
02:15:46,213 --> 02:15:49,341
Angling for a position
with the D.C.P.D. I like that.

1473
02:15:50,785 --> 02:15:53,618
Dr. Cross.
Agent Ben Devine.

1474
02:15:53,688 --> 02:15:56,555
Agent Devine is security
systems supervisor.

1475
02:15:56,624 --> 02:15:59,058
Well. For now.

1476
02:15:59,126 --> 02:16:01,117
We're going to be thrown
to the wolves.

1477
02:16:01,195 --> 02:16:03,720
As soon as they find
Megan Rose dead in a ditch.

1478
02:16:03,798 --> 02:16:06,232
Now what makes you so sure
that's what's going to happen?

1479
02:16:06,300 --> 02:16:09,497
Me getting fired
or the girl in a ditch?

1480
02:16:09,570 --> 02:16:11,834
Sorry.

1481
02:16:11,906 --> 02:16:15,672
I'm having
a pessimistic day.

1482
02:16:15,743 --> 02:16:18,405
Tell me.

1483
02:16:18,479 --> 02:16:23,280
Soneji. Did he... did he ever show
any interest in what you do?

1484
02:16:23,351 --> 02:16:26,809
How you do it?

1485
02:16:26,887 --> 02:16:30,516
The man never talked to me.
I never talked to him.

1486
02:16:32,226 --> 02:16:35,218
Well. Thanks
for your time.

1487
02:17:13,857 --> 02:17:16,883
- Hello.
- [Thunderclap]

1488
02:17:16,960 --> 02:17:18,951
What?

1489
02:17:20,430 --> 02:17:22,489
What do you think
that is?

1490
02:17:25,803 --> 02:17:30,331
- An empty frame.
- Mm-hmm.

1491
02:17:30,407 --> 02:17:32,739
Otherwise known as...

1492
02:17:34,812 --> 02:17:38,043
[Jezzie]
A missing picture.

1493
02:17:56,767 --> 02:17:59,099
[Chattering]

1494
02:18:23,193 --> 02:18:26,959
