You onto something?

1495
02:18:48,118 --> 02:18:51,246
Our missing picture.

1496
02:18:51,321 --> 02:18:53,255
Mm-hmm.

1497
02:18:53,323 --> 02:18:58,158
Our Mr. Soneji
