02:19:38,936 --> 02:19:41,996
I would guess
we're in Soneji's home.

1507
02:19:42,072 --> 02:19:46,702
Now we're supposed to
find out where that is.

1508
02:19:46,777 --> 02:19:48,711
[Woman]
Oliver MacArthur's office.

