02:20:31,922 --> 02:20:36,985
"Mercusio.
M-E-R-C-U-S-l-O."

1522
02:20:37,060 --> 02:20:40,188
- "Fourteen... thirty-two..."
- [All] "Thirty-five..."

1523
02:20:40,263 --> 02:20:42,527
- Granville.
- Gary Soneji is also known as...

1524
02:20:42,599 --> 02:20:45,830
Mercusio. Jonathan.
1435 Granville Street.

1525
02:20:45,902 --> 02:20:48,336
Well done. Alex.

1526
02:20:48,405 --> 02:20:50,600
[Sighs]

1527
02:20:55,579 --> 02:20:59,208
[Agent] In. In. In!
[Continues. Indistinct]

1528
02:20:59,282 --> 02:21:01,216
Eyes open!

1529
02:21:02,652 --> 02:21:05,644
- There.
- [Agents Talking, Indistinct]

1530
02:21:12,295 --> 02:21:14,229
[Footsteps Running Upstairs]

1531
02:21:14,297 --> 02:21:16,629
[Agent]
Not until we get the go-ahead.

1532
02:22:18,695 --> 02:22:21,323
His surveillance
was better than ours.

1533
02:22:21,398 --> 02:22:24,390
He's been at this
for years.

1534
02:22:29,806 --> 02:22:31,797
Imagine the patience,

1535
02:22:31,875 --> 02:22:35,003
the dedication.

1536
02:22:37,280 --> 02:22:39,874
You sound like
an admirer.

1537
02:22:42,052 --> 02:22:46,716
Well. He's...
he's like a spider.

1538
02:22:50,427 --> 02:22:52,361
And I happen to
like spiders.

1539
02:22:56,800 --> 02:22:58,791
[Agent] He had
an elaborate setup here, boss.

1540
02:22:58,869 --> 02:23:00,803
Want to see how he
stayed clean at school?

1541
02:23:02,973 --> 02:23:06,534
It laminates a plastic veneer
over your hands.

1542
02:23:06,610 --> 02:23:08,942
Look at this.

1543
02:23:11,348 --> 02:23:14,943
It's foam rubber. Looks like he
was wearing prosthetic appliances.

1544
02:23:16,786 --> 02:23:20,415
I understand the Secret Service
are being cautious tonight.

1545
02:23:20,490 --> 02:23:23,425
There is speculation that a full
investigation is under way into...

1546
02:23:23,493 --> 02:23:27,054
[Boat Horn Honks]

1547
02:23:27,130 --> 02:23:29,655
[Man #2 On TV] Yes, Kevin,
one of the Secret Service agents...

1548
02:23:29,733 --> 02:23:32,258
[TVOff]

