02:29:42,675 --> 02:29:45,667
[Megan Screaming]

1619
02:29:47,279 --> 02:29:51,841
- Help! Help me!
- [Engine Revs]

1620
02:29:51,917 --> 02:29:56,547
Help. Please!
Please. Help me!

1621
02:29:56,622 --> 02:29:59,614
I'm comir!
